edu.mills.cs122.lab4

Class Solver

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mills.cs122.lab4.Solver

  • public class Solver
extends java.lang.Object
    A "solver" that tries to find a sequence of transitions from a given State to an accept state in a nondeterministic finite automaton.
